<div class="footer_dt" style="font-size:14px; line-height:18px; max-width:100%;">As seen on <a data-sc-inline="14" href="https://bestfriends.org/sanctuary/explore-sanctuary/dogtown/series">National Geographic’s DogTown</a> and the CW’s Dog Town USA. And the inspiration behind the critically acclaimed film, <a href="https://bestfriends.org/champions">The Champions.</a></div>

